latestIgtvVideos.title: Diary of an old version of myself but wiser
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Three days ago, I thought of making this video on my way back home. It took me 3 hours to get it right and film this. The initial song was Eri Sakhi, but @aadityarakheja convinced me that this song goes better with the video. I enjoyed every bit of this video, though I don’t remember the process. I hope atleast a few of you would like this. If not, that’s okay. I love it and I guess that matters the most 💃🏻

latestIgtvVideos.title: Skincare routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It has taken me a really long time to understand my skin and stick to a routine that I never knew I needed. Please do research about your skin type and what will REALLY work for you. Every skin type varies. What has worked out really well for me, wouldn’t necessarily mean it would workout for your skin too. 
As requested by many, and after giving it a thought for a very long time (really really long), I finally thought of making this video. 

Products-

Cetaphil- Gentle skin cleanser (All skin types)
Dermafique- Absolute detox (Facial cleanser) (Normal-dry)
Dermafique- All important (Skin toner)
Emolene- Cream for dry skin 
Thank you @urshaynesss for introducing me to this moisturiser. 
Nykaa- Argan oil
L’Oréal Paris- Youth Code Skin activating Ferment eye essence (nighttime)
Banjara’s- Rose water

The most beautiful campaign, with the most beautiful people❤️
Video Courtesy: Sabyasachi Calcutta

Makeup and hair by @deepa.verma.makeup
Models: @archanaakilkumar, @eugeniya.belousova, @anjalisivaraman, @priyadarshini.96, @kiara.nayantara, @vishakha_b, @__kripali, @varshita.t, @ananddixit29, @bhatarya, @anujchoudhryfc, @rabannevictor
Production: @bhavnaguptapatel for @oaktreepictures
Location courtesy: City Palace, Karauli @karaulipalace
